":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:43:30.000Z","msg":"隻隻字都明，但成篇文就睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽podcast學到唔少野，感謝樂哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688e80c51b41bfce2f1aebe13c90fdce5c3b1de0","tid":2341372,"uid":267423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:44:36.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f3954ff754fa9c013ee0d153566a2ead70962168","tid":2341372,"uid":385411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:54:05.000Z","msg":"好驚呀，點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好驚有43年投資經驗嘅契媽呃我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d56cd8fc2a645139fcb8e14437ee6df21fc1d7d","tid":2341372,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3954ff754fa9c013ee0d153566a2ead70962168","tid":2341372,"uid":385411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:54:05.000Z","msg":"好驚呀，點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好驚有43年投資經驗嘅契媽呃我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺我哋話事<br />\n我哋買到契媽升<br />\n契媽跌都喺因為我哋沽鳩佢"}]}